http://www.birt-exchange.com/devshare/designing-birt-reports/517-sample-birt-report-with-combination-chart/

This example demonstrates how a Combination Chart can be created within BIRT. In addition this example also demonstrates how to add drill to details, using internal bookmarks and the Chart Interactivity Editor.

The combination chart presents the outstanding debt for the top 5 customers in Bar Chart format with a Line series representing each customer¡¯s credit limit superimposed. The bars within the chart are then linked to order details for each customer.

The attached example was built using BIRT 2.2.2